  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nImportBlock could takes up to 162ms (this is from a test mainnet node)\r\n\r\n<img width=\"881\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-04-25 at 13 17 17\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/234190312-68df68ab-8920-47f0-a6be-bc800fe3b7d3.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\n- Add metric to track it\r\n- `recomputeForkchoiceHead` takes 130ms, a lot of tasks inside it could be done while waiting for `engine.notifyNewPayload`\r\n- `LightClientServer.onImportBlockHead` takes 30ms, right now most of nodes don't act as a LightClientServer by default, should we turn the flag to not calling this function by default? If not find a better time to call it, could be in the next event loop\r\n",
